---
// Hero: intro + photo + key metrics
---
<section class="px-6 py-16 md:py-20 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider rounded bg-red-500/20 text-red-400">Private Research</span>
    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider rounded bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">DFNB16</span>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_320px] gap-10 items-start">
    <!-- Text -->
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight">
        STRC p.(Glu1659Ala)<br/>
        <span class="text-neutral-400">Variant Pathogenicity Analysis</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          My son Michael is 4 and doesn't hear well. His genetic test says he has two broken copies of the STRC gene. 
          One is confirmed pathogenic. The other is "Variant of Uncertain Significance." That classification blocks 
          him from future gene therapy trials.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm not a geneticist. I work in technology and teach AI at universities. 
          So I used AI tools to investigate the variant myself. I found computational evidence for reclassification, 
          confirmed the position is conserved across all mammals, and discovered that standard genetic tools fail 
          for this gene due to a pseudogene. I submitted a formal reclassification request to the hospital.
        </p>
        <p>
          Then I kept going. I analyzed whether a shorter protein could fit in a single gene therapy vector. 
          I checked if CRISPR could fix the specific mutation. I wrote to researchers who pioneered STRC gene therapy. 
          I received encouraging responses.
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-500">
          This site documents everything. Every tool, every result, every step. 
          So any parent in the same situation can reproduce it. Total cost: $0.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Photo -->
    <div class="order-first md:order-last">
      <img 
        src="/images/egor-misha.jpg" 
        alt="Egor and Michael" 
        class="rounded-xl w-full md:sticky md:top-24 shadow-2xl shadow-black/50"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <p class="text-[10px] text-neutral-600 mt-2 text-center">Egor and Michael, Hong Kong</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Key metrics -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-3 mt-10">
    <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 rounded-lg p-3">
      <div class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider">AlphaMissense</div>
      <div class="text-xl font-bold text-red-400 mt-1">0.9016</div>
      <div class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 mt-0.5">Likely Pathogenic</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 rounded-lg p-3">
      <div class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider">AlphaFold pLDDT</div>
      <div class="text-xl font-bold text-green-400 mt-1">95.69</div>
      <div class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 mt-0.5">Very high confidence</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 rounded-lg p-3">
      <div class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider">REVEL</div>
      <div class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mt-1">0.65</div>
      <div class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 mt-0.5">Deleterious</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 rounded-lg p-3">
      <div class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider">gnomAD</div>
      <div class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-1">0</div>
      <div class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 mt-0.5">Absent from controls</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 rounded-lg p-3">
      <div class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Conservation</div>
      <div class="text-xl font-bold text-green-400 mt-1">9/9</div>
      <div class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 mt-0.5">Mammals conserved</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 rounded-lg p-3">
      <div class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Expert Review</div>
      <div class="text-xl font-bold text-green-400 mt-1">Positive</div>
      <div class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 mt-0.5">Shared with teams</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
